OL,3,CDisabled student travels more than 850
OL,4,Cmiles across 10 days via public buses
OL,6,FA disabled photography student has
OL,7,Fspent 10 days travelling more than 850
OL,8,Fmiles across England using public
OL,9,Fbuses to highlight the challenges
OL,10,Ffaced by disabled bus pass holders.
OL,12,FDan Bowhay, from Bishops Waltham, in
OL,13,FHampshire, used his disabled bus pass
OL,14,Fto travel from Land's End to Marshall
OL,15,FMeadows, in Berwick-upon-Tweed, a
OL,16,Fjourney which takes just over nine
OL,17,Fhours by car, and filmed his journeys.
