OL,3,CDisabled student travels more than 850
OL,4,Cmiles across 10 days via public buses
OL,6,FThe Arts University Bournemouth
OL,7,Fstudent began his journey on January
OL,8,F26 and ended it on February 6, but did
OL,9,Fnot travel on weekends because of the
OL,10,Freduced services.
OL,12,FDuring each leg of his journey, Bowhay
OL,13,Ftravelled up to 10 hours a day,
OL,14,Fincluding time in transit on a bus and
OL,15,Fwaiting for a connection.
OL,17,FDan became visually impaired aged
OL,18,Ffour, when he developed cataracts in
OL,19,Fboth eyes.
