OL,6,FIt meant his left eye was removed and
OL,7,Freplaced with a prosthetic and he has
OL,8,Flimited vision in his right eye after
OL,9,Fthe lens was replaced to treat his
OL,10,Fcataracts.
OL,12,FHis condition means he struggles with
OL,13,Fhis sight and depth perception,
OL,14,Fmeaning he is unable to drive and is
OL,15,Freliant on public transport for travel.
OL,17,FDan Bowhay said, "I am exploring what
OL,18,Flimited freedoms and independence this
OL,19,Fpass affords me."
