OL,6,FHe will soon showcase a 10-hour film
OL,7,Fdocumentary called 'Between These
OL,8,FTimes' to raise awareness about his
OL,9,F"limited freedoms" as a disabled bus
OL,10,Fpass user.
OL,12,FHe said, "I've taken this genre and
OL,13,Fused it to kind of convey this journey
OL,14,FI went on in this really slow format
OL,15,Fto show just how agonisingly slow it
OL,16,Fis to travel by bus, showing all these
OL,17,Fdelays in that long, drawn out way."
