OL,6,FHe was inspired by his own personal
OL,7,Fexperiences, saying he found it
OL,8,F'impossible' to get to his hospital
OL,9,Fappointments in Southampton without
OL,10,Fany help.
OL,12,FDan said his original ambition was to
OL,13,Ftravel to John o' Groats, however his
OL,14,Fbus pass, which is free for people who
OL,15,Fare disabled, does not cover Scotland.
