OL,4,Cmiles across 10 days via public buses
OL,6,FProblems Dan Bowhay faced during the
OL,7,Ftrip included bus delays of up to 40
OL,8,Fminutes a day, waiting times of up to
OL,9,Fa several hours for connections and
OL,10,Fdifficulties with scanning his pass,
OL,11,Fmeaning he often had to present his
OL,12,Fpass to a driver.
OL,14,FHe said more investment should go into
OL,15,Fbus services and for the "public
OL,16,Fattitude" to be more understanding of
OL,17,Fthe challenges faced by disabled
OL,18,Fpeople using public transport.
