OL,6,FOf the 26 buses Dan took during the 10-
OL,7,Fday journey, he said only three had
OL,8,Faudio and one had visual announcements
OL,9,Fto indicate the location of each stop.
OL,11,F"I had to spend a fair amount of time
OL,12,Fsort of looking out the window and
OL,13,Ftrying to work out, actually, where I
OL,14,Fam, where I need to get off," he said.
